WEBVTT

00:00.960 --> 00:02.541
Previously on Haven...

00:02.920 --> 00:04.456
-Duke Crocker.
-This is Evi.

00:04.589 --> 00:05.920
I'm Duke's wife.

00:06.257 --> 00:08.373
Somebody out there with a tattoo
wants to kill me.

00:08.718 --> 00:11.755
I’m hoping that whatever/ ﬁnd buried here
will give me the answers

00:11.888 --> 00:13.424
about how / stay alive.

00:15.224 --> 00:17.215
Doesn't exactly look like something
that's gonna save my life.

00:17.310 --> 00:18.390
What is it?

00:18.603 --> 00:20.969
-"Omnia vincit amor. "
-"Love conquers all."

00:25.610 --> 00:28.443
The good people of this community
need to know what happened here.

00:28.571 --> 00:30.277
The last thing Haven needs

00:30.406 --> 00:33.648
is the Rev and his self-righteous poison
running things.

00:33.826 --> 00:35.111
He wants to be chief?

00:35.244 --> 00:36.654
He wants to control whoever is.

00:36.829 --> 00:39.741
Nathan, your father
chose to live among the cursed.

00:40.291 --> 00:43.124
-Seek forgiveness.
-I can help you.

00:43.294 --> 00:45.626
-You help a lot of people.
-|s that why I'm here?

00:45.755 --> 00:46.790
AUDREY: / can talk to them.

00:46.923 --> 00:49.335
You're troubled, like many
of the people in Haven.

00:49.467 --> 00:50.798
And I can help them.

00:52.303 --> 00:54.635
-You can't save everyone.
-But that's why I'm here.

00:54.764 --> 00:56.880
-I need to know more about her.
-Lucy Ripley.

00:56.974 --> 00:58.305
What do you think, she your mother?

00:58.976 --> 01:00.307
I am Lucy.

